Show HN: A map based Web3 app for people to launch coffee chat by staking
text:
Hi, I just launched an app for people to launch coffee chat by staking tokens.

It is how it works: find a spot on map -> choose time and how much to stake -> launch chat -> people see chat on the map -> meet up in person -> scan your QR code -> take home reward.

If you have any feedback, feel free to comment or reach out.

Contact: jeffreylin0723@gmail.com
